## Issue before code

1. Check [ROADMAP.md](../ROADMAP.md) for the active phase.
2. Open a GitHub Issue before non-trivial work:
   - Label: `integration/oms`
   - Template: `.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/integration-task.md`
   - Include: phase number, UC-ID, acceptance criteria, required test tiers
3. Link the issue on [Project #5](https://github.com/users/iamkaranvalecha/projects/5/views/1).
4. Trivial fixes (typo, single-line doc) may skip issue — note in PR body.

### Issue title convention

```
[Phase N] Short description (UC-X)
```

Examples:
- `[Phase 1] Scaffold checkout-orchestrator v4`
- `[Phase 2] IhmsClient with observability headers (UC-3)`
- `[Phase 3] Reconciliation after order timeout`

