## Cross-repo workflow (KB-IHMS docs)

For `docs/OMS-INTEGRATION.md` and `oms-integration.mdc` updates:

1. Separate issue in KB-IHMS repo
2. Branch in KB-IHMS (user naming convention)
3. Links only — no duplicate ADR bodies in KB-IHMS
4. Point to orchestrator: DECISION-MATRIX, sequences/, AI-USAGE, 4-rule set

Orchestrator PR and KB-IHMS doc PR may land in either order but both should reference the integration milestone.

