## Emergency / hotfix

Production hotfix (post Phase 5):

1. Issue with `hotfix` label
2. Branch from main
3. Minimal fix + regression test
4. verify.sh + targeted e2e if flow touched
5. Fast-track review — still requires AI-USAGE update

