## Pre-commit checklist (agents)

1. On a feature branch (not `main`)
2. Linked issue exists and is on Project #5
3. `bash scripts/verify.sh` passes (ruff + unit + contract + component + integration)
4. `cd frontend && npm test && npm run build` when frontend changed (Phase 4+)
5. **[AI-USAGE.md](../AI-USAGE.md)** updated — see [04-documentation.mdc](04-documentation.mdc)

